ARG URL_LINUX_HEADERS=https://kernel.ubuntu.com/~kernel-ppa/mainline/v5.18/amd64/linux-headers-5.18.0-051800_5.18.0-051800.202205222030_all.deb

ENV WORKDIR /build/

RUN mkdir -p $WORKDIR

ADD . .
